725371f-a.text:
49th Avenue, north side, just east of 21st Street, across the street from the old Queens Borough Hall, showing a refreshment stand at the entrance to the I.R.T. subway.
In the background is the Queensborough Bridge.
P.L. Sparr
July 27, 1940
